00:14:50,230 --> 00:14:51,690
given all the money to you.

297
00:14:52,980 --> 00:14:54,240
You're still smiling?

298
00:14:54,330 --> 00:14:55,340
That's our

299
00:14:55,340 --> 00:14:56,400
hard-earned money

300
00:14:56,700 --> 00:14:57,420
and an old woman

301
00:14:57,420 --> 00:14:58,950
took it away just like that.

302
00:14:59,870 --> 00:15:00,930
Most importantly,

303
00:15:01,070 --> 00:15:02,930
my father still thinks it's fine.

304
00:15:03,430 --> 00:15:04,520
What is the logic?

305
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:06,660
You grew up in the Lian family.

306
00:15:06,870 --> 00:15:07,470
You should

307
00:15:08,070 --> 00:15:09,400
be used to these things.

308
00:15:09,580 --> 00:15:10,460
I really...

309
00:15:13,970 --> 00:15:16,300
Let's stop talking about useless things.

310
00:15:19,060 --> 00:15:20,520
Grandma likes you so much.

311
00:15:21,580 --> 00:15:22,980
Can you

312
00:15:24,100 --> 00:15:25,190
use your

313
00:15:25,300 --> 00:15:26,700
sweet-talking skills

314
00:15:27,460 --> 00:15:29,060
and get the money back for me?

315
00:15:32,100 --> 00:15:33,070
I'm an outsider.

316
00:15:33,590 --> 00:15:35,490
If I ask your Grandma Lian for money,

317
00:15:35,490 --> 00:15:37,100
there's no way she'll give it to me

318
00:15:37,100 --> 00:15:38,760
with how much she loves money.

319
00:15:39,060 --> 00:15:40,230
Is there really no hope

320
00:15:40,230 --> 00:15:41,980
to get the money back?

321
00:15:45,230 --> 00:15:46,890
You learn from your mistakes.

322
00:15:47,750 --> 00:15:48,890
It's better

323
00:15:49,240 --> 00:15:51,300
for Grandma Lian to take the money now

324
00:15:51,430 --> 00:15:52,500
than if she took it later

325
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:53,900
after we made more money.

326
00:15:54,220 --> 00:15:56,110
Spending some money to buy a great lesson

327
00:15:56,110 --> 00:15:57,110
is not a bad thing.

328
00:15:57,560 --> 00:15:58,200
Am I right?

329
00:15:58,850 --> 00:15:59,350
Right.

330
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:05,080
Why do I feel like I actually gained something?

331
00:16:07,460 --> 00:16:08,990
Anyway, I thought about it.

332
00:16:10,110 --> 00:16:11,390
In the long run,

333
00:16:12,190 --> 00:16:13,700
we have only one way out.

334
00:16:16,980 --> 00:16:18,240
Split from the family.

335
00:16:18,340 --> 00:16:19,220
Only after we split up

336
00:16:19,220 --> 00:16:20,460
can every penny we earn

337
00:16:20,460 --> 00:16:21,220
be mine...

338
00:16:23,170 --> 00:16:23,640
Ours.

339
00:16:23,820 --> 00:16:25,280
That's easy for you to say.

340
00:16:25,380 --> 00:16:27,230
Not only will your grandparents disagree,

341
00:16:27,230 --> 00:16:28,070
but your parents also

342
00:16:28,070 --> 00:16:28,870
won't agree.

343
00:16:29,180 --> 00:16:30,110
We still have to.

344
00:16:30,610 --> 00:16:31,740
I finally get it now.

345
00:16:32,290 --> 00:16:33,750
My parents are not stupid.

346
00:16:33,870 --> 00:16:35,200
They are always bullied

347
00:16:35,460 --> 00:16:36,580
because they are too soft-hearted

348
00:16:36,580 --> 00:16:37,780
and too sentimental.

349
00:16:38,510 --> 00:16:40,820
They are always blinded by familial love,

350
00:16:40,820 --> 00:16:41,580
but they don't know

351
00:16:41,580 --> 00:16:42,230
that some people

352
00:16:42,230 --> 00:16:44,560
don't have familial love in their hearts.

353
00:16:45,230 --> 00:16:47,030
Have you decided how to split up?

354
00:16:48,950 --> 00:16:49,940
Have you decided?

355
00:16:49,940 --> 00:16:50,420
Me?

356
00:16:51,940 --> 00:16:52,870
I'm an outsider.

357
00:16:53,470 --> 00:16:54,690
You are my family.

358
00:16:55,110 --> 00:16:56,580
I won't interfere with your family affairs.

359
00:16:56,580 --> 00:16:57,460
It's getting late.

360
00:16:57,460 --> 00:16:59,120
Go back to your room and sleep.

361
00:16:59,790 --> 00:17:00,150
Hey.

362
00:17:00,510 --> 00:17:01,700
You're so smart.

363
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:02,850
Just think a little!

364
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:05,550
Shen Nuo!

365
00:17:05,990 --> 00:17:06,599
Shen Nuo.

366
00:17:06,619 --> 00:17:07,619
Brother Shen Nuo.

367
00:17:07,980 --> 00:17:08,619
Shen Nuo.

368
00:17:09,220 --> 00:17:10,150
Think a little.

369
00:17:43,910 --> 00:17:45,300
How long will it take

370
00:17:45,930 --> 00:17:47,260
to reap the rice by hand?

371
00:17:54,860 --> 00:17:56,350
The entire family is working

372
00:17:56,350 --> 00:17:57,920
and so many eyes are watching.

373
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:58,850
Don't slack off.

374
00:18:08,680 --> 00:18:10,360
Could it be...

375
00:18:10,400 --> 00:18:11,460
Is it that obvious?

376
00:18:13,510 --> 00:18:15,400
Aren't you a farmer from the Shen Village?

377
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:16,460
You had so much land

378
00:18:17,230 --> 00:18:19,430
and you don't even know how to reap rice?

379
00:18:22,540 --> 00:18:23,470
Let me teach you.

380
00:18:26,030 --> 00:18:26,830
Grab a handful

381
00:18:27,230 --> 00:18:28,870
and cut it off around five fingers' width

382
00:18:28,870 --> 00:18:29,800
from the ground.

383
00:18:30,150 --> 00:18:31,950
Be careful not to hurt your hand.

384
00:18:32,920 --> 00:18:33,980
Your hands are big.

385
00:18:34,540 --> 00:18:36,070
It's fine to grab more at a time.

386
00:18:36,070 --> 00:18:36,540
Look.

387
00:18:37,710 --> 00:18:38,440
Easy, right?

388
00:19:11,070 --> 00:19:11,910
Mother,

389
00:19:13,050 --> 00:19:14,180
how can you be so careless?

390
00:19:14,180 --> 00:19:15,190
You almost fell.

391
00:19:15,550 --> 00:19:16,810
Be careful of the baby.

392
00:19:16,830 --> 00:19:17,760
What did you say?

393
00:19:18,550 --> 00:19:19,060
I said

394
00:19:19,080 --> 00:19:20,880
be careful of the baby.

395
00:19:21,910 --> 00:19:22,670
Zhang,

396
00:19:23,510 --> 00:19:24,310
stop reaping.

397
00:19:24,900 --> 00:19:26,140
Go to the irrigation ridge

398
00:19:26,140 --> 00:19:27,820
and tie up the rice.

399
00:19:28,300 --> 00:19:28,830
Go ahead.

400
00:19:36,600 --> 00:19:37,800
I guess you're smart.

401
00:19:48,260 --> 00:19:48,790
Shouren,

402
00:19:49,790 --> 00:19:50,260
about what I mentioned

403
00:19:50,260 --> 00:19:51,220
a few days ago,

404
00:19:51,240 --> 00:19:52,400
have you decided?

405
00:19:53,390 --> 00:19:54,390
I'll do as you say.

406
00:19:54,670 --> 00:19:56,500
I think it's good.

407
00:19:56,790 --> 00:19:59,140
Is your wife willing too?

408
00:19:59,500 --> 00:20:00,230
Of course.

409
00:20:02,270 --> 00:20:03,490
I'll tell the family

410
00:20:04,230 --> 00:20:06,290
after we finish harvesting the rice.

411
00:20:08,870 --> 00:20:09,690
Lian Fang.

412
00:20:10,800 --> 00:20:12,840
Shouren is a scholar now,

413
00:20:13,150 --> 00:20:15,110
but he still comes back to work every year?

414
00:20:15,110 --> 00:20:15,740
I told him already.

415
00:20:15,740 --> 00:20:17,190
I told him he doesn't need to come.

416
00:20:17,190 --> 00:20:18,700
He should study hard at home,

417
00:20:18,700 --> 00:20:19,710
but he didn't listen.

418
00:20:19,710 --> 00:20:21,280
He insisted on coming to labor here.

419
00:20:21,280 --> 00:20:21,740
Father.

420
00:20:22,380 --> 00:20:23,870
If one is not filial toward their family,

421
00:20:23,870 --> 00:20:24,980
one would be nothing.

422
00:20:24,980 --> 00:20:25,910
This is my duty.

423
00:20:26,450 --> 00:20:27,900
My son is filial.

424
00:20:28,300 --> 00:20:28,970
Great.

425
00:20:29,730 --> 00:20:30,950
What's so tiring

426
00:20:30,990 --> 00:20:32,790
about the little work he's done?

427
00:20:33,790 --> 00:20:34,960
You're already late

428
00:20:35,230 --> 00:20:36,960
and you still have time to chat?

429
00:20:37,170 --> 00:20:37,710
Hurry up.

430
00:20:37,990 --> 00:20:39,320
Go work on your own land.

431
00:20:39,790 --> 00:20:40,700
Going to work?

432
00:20:41,070 --> 00:20:41,670
Yes, work.

433
00:20:42,290 --> 00:20:43,890
I don't see any filial piety.

434
00:20:43,890 --> 00:20:45,150
He just pulls his son out

435
00:20:45,150 --> 00:20:45,950
to put on an act

436
00:20:46,120 --> 00:20:48,580
and make everyone in the village is jealous.

437
00:20:49,690 --> 00:20:50,440
Later,

438
00:20:51,010 --> 00:20:52,040
that useless guy

439
00:20:52,170 --> 00:20:54,230
will definitely start complaining.

440
00:21:00,990 --> 00:21:01,790
What's wrong?

441
00:21:02,060 --> 00:21:03,390
What's wrong, Shouren?

442
00:21:03,580 --> 00:21:04,710
I sprained my ankle.

443
00:21:05,070 --> 00:21:06,410
I sprained my ankle.

444
00:21:06,430 --> 00:21:07,270
Have a seat.

445
00:21:08,390 --> 00:21:09,290
Let me take a look.

446
00:21:09,290 --> 00:21:09,900
No need.

447
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:12,150
Father, I'm okay.

448
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:14,610
Go to the cooling shed and rest.

449
00:21:15,320 --> 00:21:16,350
When the wagon comes

450
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:17,460
to transport the rice,

451
00:21:17,460 --> 00:21:18,410
you can go home with it.

452
00:21:18,410 --> 00:21:20,130
You don't have to come tomorrow.

453
00:21:20,130 --> 00:21:21,190
-No, no.
-Go ahead.

454
00:21:21,220 --> 00:21:22,550
Father, I can do it.

455
00:21:22,550 --> 00:21:23,070
Go rest.

456
00:21:23,070 --> 00:21:24,140
Father, I'm fine.

457
00:21:24,230 --> 00:21:24,760
Shouren.

458
00:21:24,980 --> 00:21:25,510
Shouren,

459
00:21:25,990 --> 00:21:27,250
just do as Father says.

460
00:21:27,360 --> 00:21:28,090
Shouyi and I

461
00:21:28,110 --> 00:21:29,570
can take care of the field.

462
00:21:30,530 --> 00:21:31,050
Go.

463
00:21:31,520 --> 00:21:32,950
Look at this.

464
00:21:35,280 --> 00:21:35,950
I'm sorry.

465
00:21:36,220 --> 00:21:37,080
I'm sorry.

466
00:21:37,710 --> 00:21:39,040
I'm counting on you two.

467
00:21:39,390 --> 00:21:40,050
Be careful.

468
00:21:41,220 --> 00:21:42,420
Be careful, Shouren.

469
00:21:47,590 --> 00:21:49,190
Another limping man at home.

470
00:21:53,790 --> 00:21:55,720
What's wrong? Are you limping too?

471
00:21:57,250 --> 00:21:58,510
What's wrong, Father?

472
00:21:58,870 --> 00:21:59,600
My goodness.

473
00:22:00,020 --> 00:22:00,760
Shouyi.

474
00:22:00,950 --> 00:22:01,410
Father!

475
00:22:01,750 --> 00:22:03,030
Father, look at him.

476
00:22:03,790 --> 00:22:06,180
If you're still breathing, then you can work.

477
00:22:06,180 --> 00:22:08,310
We must finish reaping these few days.

478
00:22:08,550 --> 00:22:10,570
Otherwise, if they're completely ripe and the wind blows,

479
00:22:10,570 --> 00:22:11,120
they'll drop to the ground.

480
00:22:11,120 --> 00:22:12,610
Will you two pick up the grains?

481
00:22:12,610 --> 00:22:14,010
How come Shouren can rest

482
00:22:14,210 --> 00:22:14,880
after he sprains his ankle?

483
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:15,760
Yes, look.

484
00:22:15,780 --> 00:22:17,440
Can you compare with Shouren?

485
00:22:17,500 --> 00:22:18,150
Shouren

486
00:22:18,180 --> 00:22:19,580
is a scholar.

487
00:22:19,900 --> 00:22:22,400
You are lazy and gluttonous.

488
00:22:22,420 --> 00:22:23,010
If I let you go,

489
00:22:23,010 --> 00:22:24,440
you'll be like before

490
00:22:24,630 --> 00:22:25,230
and go to the casino

491
00:22:25,230 --> 00:22:26,330
and lose my money.

492
00:22:27,710 --> 00:22:29,240
What are you talking about?

493
00:22:30,150 --> 00:22:31,200
I'll get to work.

494
00:22:36,140 --> 00:22:37,020
-You sprained your ankle too?
-Mother.

495
00:22:37,020 --> 00:22:37,670
No.

496
00:22:37,690 --> 00:22:38,580
Oh no!

497
00:22:41,030 --> 00:22:41,640
Father.

498
00:22:41,790 --> 00:22:43,250
What's wrong with you now?

499
00:22:43,340 --> 00:22:45,000
I need to go home to the toilet.

500
00:22:45,870 --> 00:22:46,330
Mother.

501
00:22:46,940 --> 00:22:47,540
How about I

502
00:22:47,550 --> 00:22:48,240
find a place for you?

503
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:49,040
Go away.

504
00:22:49,080 --> 00:22:49,520
Hurry.

505
00:22:50,780 --> 00:22:53,550
The lazy ones are always full of excuses.

506
00:22:59,790 --> 00:23:02,850
Your family really makes the capable ones work harder.

507
00:23:08,370 --> 00:23:09,270
How come

508
00:23:09,310 --> 00:23:10,740
so many seeds are moldy?

509
00:23:15,630 --> 00:23:16,430
They're back.

510
00:23:17,740 --> 00:23:18,220
Father.

511
00:23:19,100 --> 00:23:20,470
Take it slowly.

512
00:23:21,450 --> 00:23:21,910
Hua'er,

513
00:23:22,360 --> 00:23:23,810
help me back to my room.

514
00:23:24,580 --> 00:23:25,450
Father, what happened?

515
00:23:25,450 --> 00:23:26,600
I sprained my ankle.

516
00:23:29,230 --> 00:23:30,990
The harvest is great this year.

517
00:23:42,060 --> 00:23:43,180
What are you doing?

518
00:23:43,450 --> 00:23:45,110
Go away if you're not going to work.

519
00:23:45,110 --> 00:23:46,170
You might get hurt.

520
00:23:46,750 --> 00:23:47,250
You...

521
00:23:47,360 --> 00:23:48,640
Xiu'er,

522
00:23:48,980 --> 00:23:50,660
Man'er didn't do it on purpose.

523
00:23:50,660 --> 00:23:51,580
Don't be angry.

524
00:23:51,900 --> 00:23:52,550
It's too sunny out.

525
00:23:52,550 --> 00:23:53,130
Hurry,

526
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:54,040
go on inside.

527
00:23:58,550 --> 00:23:59,270
Xiu'er.

528
00:23:59,690 --> 00:24:00,220
Xiu'er,

529
00:24:00,530 --> 00:24:01,870
you're not eating sunflower seeds anymore?

530
00:24:01,870 --> 00:24:02,670
Of course not.

531
00:24:03,220 --> 00:24:04,270
Look at Lian Man'er.

532
00:24:04,270 --> 00:24:05,930
She did it on purpose just now.

533
00:24:07,670 --> 00:24:09,040
Man'er doesn't respect you

534
00:24:09,040 --> 00:24:10,000
at all.

535
00:24:10,510 --> 00:24:11,220
A few days ago,

536
00:24:11,220 --> 00:24:12,750
when Mother took her money,

537
00:24:13,090 --> 00:24:13,890
she even grabbed my hair,

538
00:24:13,890 --> 00:24:14,940
but I didn't give her a hard time.

539
00:24:14,940 --> 00:24:15,740
But look at her.

540
00:24:15,740 --> 00:24:17,600
She's giving me trouble instead.

541
00:24:18,870 --> 00:24:19,420
Xiu'er,

542
00:24:20,070 --> 00:24:21,330
you don't provoke her,

543
00:24:21,330 --> 00:24:22,060
but that doesn't stop her

544
00:24:22,060 --> 00:24:23,460
from giving you trouble.

545
00:24:24,060 --> 00:24:25,870
Your personality is too gentle.

546
00:24:26,310 --> 00:24:27,510
If you go on like this,

547
00:24:27,610 --> 00:24:29,040
you'll be bossed around

548
00:24:29,060 --> 00:24:30,920
by these juniors sooner or later.

549
00:24:31,220 --> 00:24:31,790
Yes.

550
00:24:32,060 --> 00:24:33,860
Kind people are always bullied,

551
00:24:34,860 --> 00:24:35,870
but if Man'er does this to me,

552
00:24:35,870 --> 00:24:36,800
what should I do?

553
00:24:37,230 --> 00:24:37,900
Xiu'er,

554
00:24:38,540 --> 00:24:40,110
you are too soft-hearted.

555
00:24:40,950 --> 00:24:41,500
How about

556
00:24:42,020 --> 00:24:43,280
we think of another way

557
00:24:43,850 --> 00:24:45,050
to teach her a lesson?

558
00:24:46,430 --> 00:24:47,230
But...

559
00:24:47,630 --> 00:24:49,540
We are family, after all.

560
00:24:49,940 --> 00:24:51,140
If I go overboard

561
00:24:51,270 --> 00:24:53,180
and have a huge conflict with Man'er,

562
00:24:53,180 --> 00:24:55,040
Father will definitely scold me.

563
00:24:58,220 --> 00:25:00,660
Yes, you're right.

564
00:25:02,190 --> 00:25:03,590
After all, we are family.

565
00:25:44,900 --> 00:25:46,830
I'll take care of them. Be careful.

566
00:26:08,220 --> 00:26:10,030
Please show mercy.

567
00:26:10,700 --> 00:26:11,270
I

568
00:26:11,900 --> 00:26:12,960
have a gift for you.

569
00:26:14,540 --> 00:26:15,540
Please accept it.

570
00:26:17,020 --> 00:26:18,150
Please do us a favor.

571
00:26:25,380 --> 00:26:26,520
In the past,

572
00:26:26,940 --> 00:26:29,140
these taels of silver could satisfy me,

573
00:26:29,940 --> 00:26:30,700
but today,

574
00:26:32,020 --> 00:26:33,550
I brought a lot of men along.

575
00:26:34,080 --> 00:26:35,970
Even if I want to let the goods go,

576
00:26:36,240 --> 00:26:37,910
my men won't agree.

577
00:26:40,190 --> 00:26:40,910
You're breaking

578
00:26:40,910 --> 00:26:42,170
the rules of the trade.

579
00:26:42,210 --> 00:26:42,910
Rules?

580
00:26:46,710 --> 00:26:48,180
I make the rules.

581
00:26:48,600 --> 00:26:49,190
Go!

582
00:26:49,270 --> 00:26:49,710
This...

583
00:26:49,710 --> 00:26:50,300
Go! Go!

584
00:27:04,900 --> 00:27:06,830
Stop! Stop!

585
00:27:06,920 --> 00:27:08,140
You are...

586
00:27:09,590 --> 00:27:10,450
Do you know

587
00:27:10,640 --> 00:27:12,230
whose goods you're robbing?

588
00:27:12,230 --> 00:27:13,640
It belongs to the Song family.

589
00:27:13,640 --> 00:27:15,770
The Song family is the one I'm robbing.

590
00:27:18,620 --> 00:27:20,590
