933
00:41:28,000 --> 00:41:29,570
How dare you hit her?

934
00:41:30,030 --> 00:41:30,470
I won't let you off!

935
00:41:30,470 --> 00:41:30,980
Look at me.

936
00:41:30,980 --> 00:41:31,980
