964
00:43:15,890 --> 00:43:16,950
You must be joking.

965
00:43:17,010 --> 00:43:18,460
The natural disaster came out of nowhere.

966
00:43:18,460 --> 00:43:19,860
Even the officials fled.

967
00:43:20,390 --> 00:43:21,720
